stimulusHtml: Which of the following represents the contents of  my2Darr  after executing this code segment?

features.html:
Consider the following code segment.

 

int[][] my2Darr = new int[4][3];

for (int r = 0; r < my2Darr.length; r++)
{
   for (int c = 0; c < my2Darr[0].length; c++) 
   {
      if (r == c)
      {
         my2Darr[r][c] = r;
      }
   }
}
